{
  "stem": "24462.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then Molotov was speaking over the radio-- not Stalin, Molotov.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Molotov was announcing that Germany has invaded the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And of course, we will fight and so on, so on, so on, so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "On the third of July, we saw the Germans coming in town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well, it wasn't good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They didn't start anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they took-- after a few days-- maybe a week or two-- they start taking the Jews to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And one day, I went with the group of Jews to work for the Germans or the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because the Ukrainians are mainly the, the ones who were in charge.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was beating and shoving.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, and, and, it was-- nobody was killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But still, it was the atmosphere, well, you are not a human being anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You are absolutely not human being.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They can do with you whatever they, they want.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And next time when we were called by the Jewish [INAUDIBLE], is anybody the Jewish [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], the Jewish authority.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was some kind of Jewish authority in town-- to come to work, I said to my friend, a friend of mine, I'm not going.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, why don't you go?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I listen, I can see this terrible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I am trying to escape.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said to me, listen, what will happen to all the Jews will happen to us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We will go all together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was-- I wasn't very, very excited about this and already convinced that I can do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I still did-- said, I can't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I started looking for a place how to escape.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I found some Ukrainians who-- first thing, I wasn't wearing the Jewish, whatever they were wearing then.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
